{"title":"今日北京","authors":["黄文欢"],"dates":[{"year":1979,"month":9,"day":29}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"今日北京"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黄文欢"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三十年前一旧城，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"而今万象喜新生。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"楼如崇岭参天立，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"车似游龙满地行。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"白叟黄童多笑色，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"通衢僻巷溢歌声。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"君如不信吾言是，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"请且抽空到北京。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一九七九年九月二十八日"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"新华社发的这首诗，是黄文欢同志二十八日在北京用中文写的。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"·编者·"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":4,"page_end":4}